# 🚀 Static Routing using SDN Controller (Mininet + Ryu)

## 📌 Overview

This project demonstrates **static routing in Software Defined Networking (SDN)** using Mininet and Ryu Controller. It implements manual OpenFlow rules to establish fixed packet forwarding paths and validates network performance through connectivity, flow table, and throughput testing.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

* **Mininet** – Network simulation
* **Ryu Controller** – SDN controller
* **OpenFlow v1.3** – Controller-switch communication
* **Linux / Ubuntu Terminal**

